Stark Says Governments Should do Homework Before Giving Advice

-- B y   G a b i   T h e s i n g
-- 
2011-09-24T21:21:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-24/stark-says-governments-should-do-homework-before-giving-advice.html
European Central Bank Executive
Board member Juergen Stark said “all governments should do
their homework before they give advice” to other countries and
regions. Stark commented in a panel discussion in  Washington .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
